text: Comedy Big League () is a South Korean comedy show presenting Shin Young-il and Bae Ji-hyun. It airs on tvN on Sundays at 19:45(KST). ==Seasons== *Season 1 (September 17, 2011 - November 19, 2011) *Season 2 (December 24, 2011 - March 31, 2012) *Season 3 (May 12, 2012 - August 18, 2012) *Season 4 (September 29, 2012 - August 17, 2013) *Season 5 (September 29, 2013 – present) ==Famous Comedians== *Park Na-rae *Lee Guk-joo *Lee Yong-jin *Lee Jin-ho *Lee Sang-jun *Yang Se-hyung *Yang Se-chan *Yoo Sang-moo *Jang Dong-min *Jang Do-yeon *Jo Se-ho ==Awards and nominations== {| class=wikitable |- !
